      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a dedicated project car or a source for spare parts. The exterior shows significant neglect, with extensive rust perforating the wheel wells and rocker panels, alongside several deep scratches and a large dent on the rear passenger door. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The interior has heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing is recommended for transport.",
