      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a solid car for me\u2014super dependable and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s in really nice shape and is perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle that's ready to go. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it's definitely ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
