    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including subframe reinforcement and upgraded bushings for precise handling. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and suspension remain dialed for performance, offering a communicative driving experience through its hydraulic steering rack and tuned MacPherson/multi-link setup.",
      "price": 33500.0,
