    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury sedan that perfectly balances executive comfort with spirited performance. Finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic over a Black Dakota leather interior, the car presents beautifully. On the exterior, the paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on one wheel reflect its honest history as a daily commuter. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker sanctuary; the leather seats show only light, natural creasing on the driver's bolster, and the wood trim remains free of cracks or fading. Every feature\u2014from the heated multi-contour seats and power sunroof to the premium Harman Kardon surround sound system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook, featuring a complete service log. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power, and the xDrive all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all weather conditions. It comes with two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and recent service records, making it a turnkey choice for a buyer who appreciates a high-quality, well-documented vehicle.",
